    h3 Multiple Layered Icons
    p You can also specify layered icons, specified from bottom up, with each also supporting optional CSS classes.
    pre
      span.bold.red %fam/
      | icon-name
      span.bold.red
        | :
      | css
      span.bold.red
        | ;
      | icon-name
      span.bold.red
        | /

    h3 Icons in Links
    p These icons can also be used in links.
    pre
      span.bold.red
        | [%fa/
      | users
      span.bold.red
        | :
      | red
      span.bold.red
        | /](
      | /users
      span.bold.red
        | )
    hr

