    h2 Comments
    p You can mark an entire paragraph as a comment. Comments will be removed before rendering the page.
    p These can be helpful if you want to temporarily change a page, but want to remember what it had before.
    pre
      span.bold.red
        ' //
      span.gray This is a comment.
